{"badges":["TM5","TM6"],"preparations":[{"content":["Place water into mixing bowl. Insert simmering basket, then weigh peas, broad beans and edamame into it. Add garlic to simmering basket and cook <b>10 min\/Varoma\/speed 2<b>.","Remove simmering basket with aid of spatula and set aside to cool for 10-15 minutes. Remove the outer shells from broad beans and, if using frozen edamame beans, remove edamame from pods (see tips). Empty mixing bowl.","Place spring onion\/shallot, mint, avocado, reserved cooled garlic and ¾ of the cooled peas and beans into mixing bowl and chop <b>3 sec\/speed 7<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula, then mix <b>3 sec\/speed 5<b>. Scrape down sides of mixing bowl with spatula again.","Add all remaining ingredients, including remaining ¼ of the cooled beans and peas, and combine <b>3 sec\/\/speed 4<b>. Transfer into a serving bowl and serve immediately or cover and place into refrigerator until ready to serve."]}],"ingredients":[{"title":"","content":["500 g water","100 g fresh green peas, shelled","50 g fresh broad beans, shelled","50 g fresh edamame  beans, shelled","2 garlic cloves","1 spring onion\/shallot, trimmed and cut into halves","1 sprig fresh mint, leaves only","1 avocado, flesh only","50 g feta cheese, cut into pieces (1 cm)","1 tsp lemon juice, to taste","½ - 1 tsp jarred horseradish, to taste (optional)"]}],"id":"r93915","imageLink":"https:\/\/3.bp.blogspot.com\/-mp01BKx0t_o\/XZaf0z5bBQI\/AAAAAAAAgyg\/33fT7_6dt9UG6lj7d1fqS3pj62WKRH9JgCLcBGAsYHQ\/s1600\/0_wvKeL0eYob-mxj5y.png","title":"Smashed pea and bean dip","publishedAt":"2015-12-14T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"4 g","fat":"9 g","uom":"per 50 g","carbohydrates":"2 g","calories":"467 kJ \/ 111 kcal"},"usefulItems":"plastic wrap, serving bowl, refrigerator","hintsAndTricks":["Frozen edamame beans will come in their pods so you will need to use double the quantity (100 g) and then shell the beans after cooling in step 2.","If you have trouble sourcing edamame beans, substitute with more beans or peas."],"basicInfo":["easy","10m","30m","375 g"]}